<table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4"><tr bgcolor="#000000"><td><font color="#FFFFFF"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial" size="6">Trust your Noble Steed...</font></td></tr></table><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0"><tr><td></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Author</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">skitch</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Description</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Modern Day Trust drop the Dunland Bomb all over the place.</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Cards</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Frodo, Tired Traveller<br />
The One Ring, Answer to All Riddles<br />
<br />
Sites<br />
1. Play Aragorn from your draw deck<br />
2. No Dunland Archery Wounds<br />
3. No Dunland Archery Wounds<br />
4. Heal each Mounted Companion<br />
5. Play Saruman from draw deck<br />
6. Play a possession to draw a card<br />
7. Spot a Rohan man or exert everyone<br />
8. Play a Dunlender to draw a card<br />
9. Play Saruman from discard pile for -2<br />
<br />
